OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,F15th February marks the 55th
OL,7,Fanniversary of one of the biggest
OL,8,Fchanges Britain has ever gone through.
OL,10,F15th February 1971 was known as D Day `
OL,11,Fit was the day when decimal money
OL,12,Freplaced the old system of shillings
OL,13,Fand pence.
OL,15,FIreland also went decimal on the same
OL,16,Fday.
OL,18,FIt was a complicated change for
OL,19,Fbusinesses to handle. A number of adult
OL,20,Feducation films were shown on BBC TV in
OL,21,Fthe weeks beforehand, one of which was
OL,22,Fentitled Training for D Day.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,158,140,200,120,0,100
