OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F157A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt was shown at 9am each morning in the
OL,7,Fweek before decimalisation.
OL,9,FBut from a consumer point of view, you
OL,10,Fmight imagine it was a straightforward
OL,11,Fchange. A complex system was being
OL,12,Freplaced by one which was logical and
OL,13,Fstraightforward.
OL,15,FIn fact some older and vulnerable
OL,16,Fpeople found the change difficult. Some
OL,17,Fwere anxious or tried to resist.
OL,19,FA lengthy public information film was
OL,20,Fmade with them in mind.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,158,140,200,120,0,100
