OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt was called Granny Gets the Point and
OL,7,Fwas shown regularly as a scheduled
OL,8,Fprogramme in many ITV regions. You can
OL,9,Fsee it on YouTube.
OL,11,FThere were intense preparations for
OL,12,Fdecimalisation over several years.
OL,14,F5p and 10p pieces ` identical in value
OL,15,Fand size to 1/- and 2/- pieces ` were
OL,16,Fin circulation from 1968. The following
OL,17,Fyear 50p pieces came into use. And a
OL,18,Fpound, of course , was still a pound.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,158,140,200,120,0,100
